that God has a plan for me.

955
01:18:11,282 --> 01:18:13,477
A plan for all of us.

956
01:18:16,120 --> 01:18:18,645
Please.

957
01:18:21,525 --> 01:18:23,550
Simon...

958
01:18:29,333 --> 01:18:31,267
