1079
01:31:15,906 --> 01:31:18,129
Up we go.

1080
01:31:18,200 --> 01:31:20,134
Thanks.

1081
01:32:04,747 --> 01:32:07,580
You okay?

1082
01:32:07,650 --> 01:32:10,619
You okay?

1083
01:32:15,257 --> 01:32:18,158
I was thinking.

1084
01:32:18,227 --> 01:32:20,388
Maybe this was
your destiny.

1085
