over 200 Mississippi.

1173
01:44:43,505 --> 01:44:47,373
Nobody likes a showoff.

1174
01:44:47,442 --> 01:44:49,637
Promise me.

1175
01:44:49,711 --> 01:44:52,305
Yeah.

1176
01:44:52,381 --> 01:44:54,679
